      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLD STRIPES (1) ran well two back when hitting the frame then out of the placings at Warrnambool latest but returns to a course where he has performed well. Meets a moderate line up and rates on top this time. LAKEVIEW MITCH (5) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (22.89) in a Grade 5 at Geelong. Has a good record here including two wins. Leading chance. BRAGGING RIGHTS (2) comes off an average performance last start when fifth at Warrnambool over 390m behind Black Business (22.97) in a Grade 5 H. Was in the money the start prior. Form from his last run is proving very strong. Has ability and can measure up. BLAME MARGARET (3) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.",
